 "remarks": "Welcome to 7 Hamilton Ave, SoNo&apos;s hidden gem and a commuter&apos;s dream! Perfectly situated just a short walk from the South Norwalk train station and everything vibrant SoNo has to offer, this spacious top-floor 2-bedroom condo combines convenience, comfort, and privacy.  Enjoy peaceful, tree-lined views along with an abundance of natural light throughout the home&apos;s open and inviting floor plan. The recently updated kitchen and beautifully renovated bathroom featuring a deep soaking tub add modern style and functionality, while high-efficiency insulated windows and a newer sliding glass door enhance comfort year-round.  Additional highlights include a full-size washer and dryer conveniently located in the unit, plus a private balcony off the living area-the perfect spot to relax and enjoy the warmer months. A dedicated storage space in the building&apos;s storage room provides added convenience and extra room for your belongings. The building itself has also undergone both interior and exterior improvements, offering added appeal and peace of mind.  7 Hamilton Ave comes complete with 2 reserved parking spaces (#1 and #18), this home offers the ideal blend of location, updates, and lifestyle in the heart of Norwalk. Come create new memories at 7 Hamilton Ave.",
